5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","Wolffdene"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in Wolffdene? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across Wolffdene, Beenleigh, Ormeau and Stapylton. Our 5-star instructors help Wolffdene students pass their Queensland driving test on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Wolffdene is a quiet semi-rural locality on the outer border between Logan and the Gold Coast hinterland — a genuinely peaceful road environment with very low traffic volumes and the characteristic open sightlines of the Logan–Gold Coast rural corridor. For learner drivers, Wolffdene's local roads provide one of south-east Queensland's most relaxed and gentle starting environments for the driving learning experience."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"Our instructors connect the calm local roads of Wolffdene progressively northward to Beenleigh and southward to Ormeau — building the suburban, arterial, and motorway-adjacent road experience that Queensland's practical assessment covers. The geographic positioning between two established urban centres means Wolffdene learners naturally encounter a very broad range of road types across their lesson program."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Wolffdene learners test at the Browns Plains Transport and Main Roads Centre. Free pickup from Wolffdene, Afterpay available. Book today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-100 flex items-start gap-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-primar